column2: a passenger car that was initially stopped in front of the waymo av facing northwest in the second to the right lane began to reverse. the waymo av came to a stop in the queue of traffic with its rear left side still partially in the second to right lane. the passenger car continued to reverse and the rear right side of the passenger car made contact with the rear left side of the stationary waymo av. at the time of the impact
column3: the waymo av’s level 4 ads was engaged in autonomous mode. the waymo av sustained damage.
